    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and some minor paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but the engine has a minor oil leak and the suspension feels a bit loose, suggesting that some bushings or struts may need replacement soon. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable vehicle who doesn't mind performing some light maintenance and cosmetic touch-ups.",
