    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver. Featuring a clean profile and a robust mechanical foundation, it has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure peak operational performance. The interior remains remarkably preserved, offering a refined environment that balances modern comfort with enduring quality. For those seeking a dependable, high-caliber driving experience, this offering stands as a testament to conscientious ownership and sustained value.",
      "price": 36450.0,
