      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today! It's been well-loved, runs like a charm, and has plenty of adventures left in it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
